author: @iammdla
text:
Dear Jimin,

I hope that when you read this letter, you are well, happy, and full of energy. I want you to know that your smile and your talent brighten my life every day. You are a constant inspiration to me, not only because of your music and art but also because of the humble, kind, and hardworking person you are.

Thank you for coming into my life during difficult times and for healing my wounds with your voice and presence. Your effort and dedication motivate me to be better and never give up. I admire how you always give your best, even when you push yourself hard, and that teaches me to fight for my dreams with the same passion.

I wouldn’t change anything about you because every part of who you are is perfect and unique. Thank you for existing and for being a beacon of light for me and millions of people. Even though I can’t see you in person, I will always be supporting you and celebrating your achievements from afar.

With all my love and admiration,
멜리사 ♡

author: @Smartandlonely
text:
Dear Jimin, Jiminie, Jiminshi, Chim Chim, Baby Mochi and etc; 

I wanted to write something about you, with the hope that one day you will read what I wrote. 

Each member is very precious, their individual talents are indisputable. But even RM has said many times that the person who attracted the most attention during BTS  first stage debut was you Jiminie. You made BTS more well-known. You have always been at an important place for BTS with your dance breaks and appearance in the most important parts of the songs. (No more dreams, we are bulletproof, N.O., fire, blood sweat and tears, not today, black swan...)  In later periods, you have always been the most notable member with your unique dances, visual and courage. 

What I want to tell you is that we didn't love you just because of your beautiful voice. We loved you for your unique dancing talent, which no one else has, which has always enabled you to be at the top of the "best kpop dancers ever" lists. 

We loved you for your eye-catching stage performances and perfect stage presence. 

We loved you for your fun personality that fills everywhere you enter with joy, your perfect smile that is out of this world, and your laughter that warms our hearts. 

We loved you because you thought about everyone (A.R.M.Y, members, family, friends...) more than yourself. We loved you because we know how humble and helpful you are. 

All we want from you is that ; you love yourself as much as we love you. It makes us very sad that you have been so insecure about yourself and always blamed yourself just because of your voice for years. Please know that you are not just about your vocal talent. 

I hope you take care of yourself in the military and return to your fans waiting for you as soon as possible. 

I love you very much my dear Jiminie ❤️

author: @dandy_97
text:
Prácticamente me estuve aguantando las ganas de llorar en todo el vídeo, los tiempos extensos de práctica y de seguro tenía otros trabajos que tenía que hacer aparte de los ensayos, pocas horas de sueño, largas jornadas sin comer más se le suma el hecho de que estaba a dieta y no podía comer lo que se le antojara, el cansancio acumulado más del hecho de sufrir de espasmos musculares cuando sobre exige su cuerpo, Jimin lo dio todo para presentarnos un gran álbum y unas excelentes presentaciones, agradezco mucho a Jimin por que con su álbum se sincero con nosotros y nos contó su verdad de lo que había vivido en la pandemia, él nos entregó parte de su alma en ese álbum expresado en letras y danzas. Yo solo espero que nadie tome a la ligera el álbum de Jimin, como también el de Namjoon por que él también entrego parte de su alma en su álbum en el transcurso de sus 20s y Hobi ya que su álbum trata de una crítica a los seres humanos y a los hechos que son reales del día a día, que debemos parar con la crítica, respetar los ideales de los demás y auto analizarte a tí mismo que es lo que quieres y deseas. En verdad mis respetos a los chicos son grandiosos artistas.
Posdata: Jimin yo se que somos ARMY pero esa forma de despedirte en el vídeo me angustia, aunque yo sé que te debes ir al SM, no se si lo hiciste para ir procesando el hecho que de todos modos no te vamos a ver tan seguido durante 18 meses.
Posdata 2: deleitarme con la belleza natural de Jimin es mi pasión y felicidad, hay como le quisiera dar una abrazo a este hombre.

Jin and Jimin, members of BTS, achieve more records on various charts and music platforms 🖤🔥:

✨ Jimin became the first soloist in K-Pop history to top the US Billboard Artist 100 chart

✨ Jin's "The Astronaut" became the longest-running K-pop solo song on the Billboard world digital sales chart of the decade, with a total of 13 weeks on the chart.

✨ JIN'S FACE joins BTS' MOTS:7 as the only albums in K-Pop history to spend 11 or more days at the top of the iTunes World Albums Chart

✨ The Astronaut song by Jane has crossed the 11M search mark on the Shazam app, making it the fastest song by an Asian artist to achieve this milestone in the history of the platform.

✨Jimin joins fellow band member Jungkook as the only Korean singles in history to have their Spotify accounts surpass 12.7M monthly streams.

PS It's fun to get this little glimpse into the past - the hard work before the Billboard #1, Kookie's notably new cap and denim by a certain designer...
..

text:
僕らは出来上がった物を見て

凄い！
かっこいい！
素晴らしい！

って思い、
言葉を発してしまうけど...

疲れていようが
忙しかろうが
視聴者に喜んでもらう為に
最後の最後まで妥協なく、

血と汗の滲む練習を重ねに重ねて、
こういった傑作を作り上げている事に、
ジミンのその実直な姿勢に凄く感動した。

BTSは数曲しか知らないし、
メンバーの顔と名前も一致出来ないニワカファンだけど、ジミンのダンスが好きってだけで、ジミンだけは他のメンバーよりもアンテナ張れてたからか、
たまたまこのソロの「Like Crazy」を耳にし、久しぶりに体に衝撃が走った。

こんなに素晴らしい作品を提供してくれて、ほんとにありがとう。

ただ、
ジミンの体が心配...

１つの大仕事を仕上げたあとは、
存分に体を休ませて、
心身共に十分リフレッシュして欲しい。
